descriptionNullable:
This dataset contains information about **Students' Mental issues** with different attributes.
We collected this information from various students and we analyzed where the students are facing more mental issues.

These are **18** different attributes or columns.
-> Timestamp
-> Gender	
-> Age	
-> Department	
-> Are_you_happy_with_your_department_work_area	
-> Why_did_you_chosen_your_department_work_area	
-> Current_year_you_are_studying_in	
-> Cgpa	
-> Are_you_having_proper_sleep_everyday	
-> How_much_time_are_you_sleeping_everyday	
-> Are_you_getting_good_food_diet_everyday	
-> What_is_your_screen_time	
-> On_what_do_you_spend_your_screen_time_more	
-> From_where_you_are_getting_stress
-> When_you_are_stressed_more
-> What_will_you_like_to_do_when_you_are_stressed	
-> How_did_you_felt_during_COVID_19_pandemic_period	
-> concentrate_on_your_work_when_you_are_stressed
